Package com.cyberfront.crdt.operation

Class OperationManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyberfront.crdt.operation.OperationManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<OperationManager>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GenericOperationManager
    public class OperationManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<OperationManager>
    This is the base class for wrapping AbstractOperations. It provides the basic functionality for associating various elements of metadata associated with the op bound to the derived manager class.
